#YourTampaExpert is thrilled to introduce 12205 Broadwater Loop to the market. I am representing the seller on the sale of this gorgeous, classical estate in the prestigious #StonelakeRanch Community. 

Listed for $2,250,000 this home has a few unique features that make it a particularly compelling opportunity but I’ll let the pictures do the talking. 7000 square feet of living space, 5 bedrooms and 6.5 bathrooms, sitting on just shy of two acres and 170 feet of lake frontage… with a boat dock and two jet ski lifts… Who is going to have the pleasure of making memories here?

Representing the seller and just put 12205 BROADWATER LOOP #UnderContract with only 6 active days on the market. Another deal in the Stonelake Ranch community of Thonotosassa!

Last available for $2,250,000.00.

By highlighting the sanctuary-like setting of the neighborhood, construction quality, and architectural details we were able to generate a multiple offer situation.

If you have a home you are looking to sell in the Greater Tampa Bay Area or are a buyer looking for pre-market properties in this area, please text message #YourTampaExpert at 813-737-7091 to set up a consultation!

PS: I have the inside scoop on another #OFFMARKET home in the #StonelakeRanch community, this one is closer to 9000 living square feet, has a 10++ CAR GARAGE, and sits on nearly 8 ACRES. It will be priced in excess of $3 million.

#OhHelloThere! I'm beyond grateful to add another luxury home sale to my resume! Recently, I had the privilege to sell 12205 Broadwater Loop in Thonotosassa, FL, for $2,300,000 - $50,000 above the asking price. This is one of my highest sales ever, and I couldn't have done it without the support of my friends, especially those on social media. Your referrals and support have helped me build my business and reputation to do deals like this, and for that, I'm truly grateful.

This Mediterranean beauty, built by Alvarez Homes in 2008, is located in the prestigious Stonelake Ranch community and boasts unique features like 1.8 acres of land, 170 feet of water frontage with access to Lake Thonotosassa, and a dock with a 10,000 pound boat lift & 2 jet ski lifts.

I'm humbled to have navigated inspection negotiations without giving any credits/price reductions, created a multiple offer situation, and defended the value of the home to the bank appraiser.

If you're looking to buy or sell a similar property (or something completely different) feel free to reach out to me via text/call at 813-737-7091. #MillionDollarListing #SellingTampa #YourTampaExpert #GratefulForYourSupport

Photo-dump alert! 📸 Here's a little chronicle of my recent adventures: celebrating my 29th birthday at Persia House of Kabob with the restaurant owner , attending my dear friend Ibrahim and Salma's beautiful wedding in Tampa, and sharing some random shots from my ongoing Australia honeymoon. 

Sydney has been an absolute dream, from visiting the iconic Sydney Opera House and climbing the bridge, to strolling along the breathtaking coastal walk from Bronti to Coogee beach. And of course, indulging in some delicious Iranian, Pakistani, and Chinese cuisine! 

Along the way, I've met some amazing people, including a Bangladeshi mechanical engineer turned cab driver and a native Australian cabbie who's a big fan of Muhammad Ali and Elvis Presley. Now, it's time for some diving adventures in Cairns! 🌊

Kangaroo Island, you stole my heart 💙 The crystal-clear waters on the South Australia coastline, the lush greenery, and the hills made for a perfect getaway. And let’s not forget about the kangaroo sightings, which added to the magic of this place! 🦘 

Getting to our vacation home was quite the adventure - the unpaved, steep road was treacherous, and we felt so removed from civilization. But it was all worth it! 🌅 Plus, nothing beats cooking lamb hot dogs on the outdoor grill while taking in the breathtaking views. 🌭 #KangarooIsland #SouthAustralia #VacationGoals #NatureLovers #KangarooSightings #GrillMaster

Last Australia photo dump. From Iranian kebabs in Sydney to helicopter rides over the majestic Uluru, and scuba diving in the Great Barrier Reef, our honeymoon  was nothing short of magical! 🌟 

And let's not forget about the unforgettable experience of spotting wild kangaroos and cuddly koalas on Kangaroo Island. 🦘🐨 

The 24+ hours of travel from Tampa were more than worth it to experience this underrated destination with diverse and kind people, laid-back lifestyle, and natural beauty that took our breath away. 💕 #Honeymoon #Australia #TravelGoals #Uluru #GreatBarrierReef #KangarooIsland #WildlifeSpotting #kebabs
Good, because I needed a psychiatrist ✅
